ivardefs.name: canPushUpdates
ivardefs.desc: Ability of the primary source to push updates/alerts (yes; no; undetermined).

ivardefs.name: communicationMethod_
ivardefs.desc: Method for communicating with the primary source (manual; API; Push).

ivardefs.name: pushTypeAvailable_
ivardefs.desc: Type of alerts/updates the primary source can send (specific requested changes; any changes; as defined by source).

ivardefs.name: type_
ivardefs.desc: Type of primary source (License Board; Primary Education; Continuing Education; Postal Service; Relationship owner; Registration Authority; legal source; issuing source; authoritative source).

ivardefs.name: validationDate
ivardefs.desc: When the target was validated against the primary source.

ivardefs.name: validationStatus
ivardefs.desc: Status of the validation of the target against the primary source (successful; failed; unknown).

properties.desc: Information about the primary source(s) involved in validation.
